Privacy Policy / 隐私政策

Last updated: 2026.6.10

XiYing Crypto ("the App") respects your privacy. This policy explains how we handle information.

1. Information We Collect
The App does NOT collect, store, or transmit any personal information. We do not require account registration, and we do not track your identity.

2. Watchlist Data
Your custom watchlist is stored locally on your device only. It is never uploaded to any server.

3. Third-Party Data Sources
The App displays public market data retrieved from third-party APIs (such as CoinGecko). These requests do not include any personal information about you.

4. No Analytics or Advertising
The App contains no third-party analytics, tracking, or advertising SDKs.

5. Children's Privacy
The App is not directed to children under 13 and does not knowingly collect data from them.

6. Changes
We may update this policy. Changes will be posted on this page.

7. Contact
For questions, contact: amwpessy@gmail.com

